; Regression test for issue #1092: balance assignments processed in parse
; order rather than date order.
;
; When the $30 transfer (dated July 20) appears in the file BEFORE the
; balance assignment (dated July 10), the assignment should still evaluate
; against an empty account balance — not the $30 already parsed — because
; July 10 precedes July 20 chronologically.

2014/07/20 Transfer
    Expenses:Misc                            $30.00
    Liabilities:Test

2014/07/10 Opening Balance
    Liabilities:Test                    = $-200.00
    Equity:Opening Balances

test bal
             $200.00  Equity:Opening Balances
              $30.00  Expenses:Misc
            $-230.00  Liabilities:Test
--------------------
                   0
end test
